Venizelos Says Greek Citizens Are Aware of the Situation

-- B y   N a t a l i e   W e e k s   a n d   M a r i a   P e t r a k i s
-- 
2011-09-18T17:53:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-18/venizelos-says-greek-citizens-are-aware-of-the-situation.html
Greek Finance Minister Evangelos
Venizelos said every Greek was fully aware of the seriousness of
the situation facing them. He spoke in comments televised live
on state-run NET TV today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Natalie Weeks in Athens at 
 nweeks2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
